            THE AMIGA PUNTER

Can your computer help you in picking winners at Randwick, Flemington, 
wherever?

Well, yes! Perhaps. Maybe........ but then again, who knows?

----------------------------------------------------------------------

From the outset let me say that you should not take this program 
seriously. Consequently, be aware that I make no claims about the
validity of the theories, equations and general guesswork used by the
AMIGAPUNT program to rate race-horses.

I DO NOT ACCEPT ANY RESPONSIBILITY FOR LOSSES, DAMAGES, INABILITY TO 
TO PAY THE RENT, MARITAL BREAK UP, OR  ANY OTHER CATASTROPHES THAT 
MAY RESULT, DIRECTLY OR INDIRECTLY  FROM THE USE OF 'AMIGAPUNT'.

                     D I S T R I B U T I O N.

